reviews.text: Always long Q. Go this doctor because the medication work on me. I always have migraine & this medicine is good. After take i can feel better. Not so pain anymore.

This clinic always has the best service & medication prescribtion! Dr Dina is always very kind & patient always. Been coming to this clinic for as long as I can remember & it always health me up quickly. Thank you! (:

Doctor Quek is very patient and nice! This clinic is always my first choice when I’m sick, not only because it is near to my house but also their good services. Before that they only accept cash, now can scan to pay! More convenient for ppl like me

Dr Dina is the best doctor I've ever had. I've been going to her for the past 5 or more years already. She thoroughly explains every diagnosis properly and gives the best advice on how to take care of my health better. She's extremely attentive to her patients. She doesn't rush through her consultations and takes time to explain and this makes me feel safe and assured with her.

She's my family's go-to doctor everytime. I have a company subsidised doctor just a walking distance away where I can get company sponsored consultation and prescriptions but I always go to Dr Dina everytime. Simply because she's the best. Thanks Dr Dina! ❤️
I had a very pleasant experience visiting the clinic. The staff were friendly & patient. Dr Dina was excellent! She's patient and clear in explaining.
